Project Firefly is a cloud-native, serverless application development platform provided by Adobe. It allows developers to quickly build and deploy custom applications, websites, and services using Adobe's infrastructure and services.

OpenAI is an artificial intelligence research laboratory and company that aims to advance artificial intelligence in a safe and beneficial way for humanity. It was founded in December 2015 by Elon Musk, Sam Altman, Greg Brockman, Ilya Sutskever, Wojciech Zaremba, and John Schulman.
